1 AN ACT
2 RELATING TO INSURANCE; AMENDING THE GROUP INSURANCE
3 CONTRIBUTIONS FOR SCHOOL DISTRICTS AND CHARTER SCHOOLS;
4 ELIMINATING WAIVERS FOR SCHOOL DISTRICT AND CHARTER SCHOOL
5 PARTICIPATION IN PUBLIC SCHOOL INSURANCE AUTHORITY HEALTH,
6 DISABILITY INCOME AND TERM LIFE PLANS; REQUIRING REFERENCE-
7 BASED PRICING; REQUIRING A STUDY OF THE SUSTAINABILITY OF
8 INSURANCE PROGRAMS FOR PUBLIC SCHOOL EMPLOYEES.
9
10 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF NEW MEXICO:
11 SECTION 1. Section 10-7-4 NMSA 1978 (being Laws 1941,
12 Chapter 188, Section 1, as amended) is amended to read:
